Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你不一样 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想斩断已有的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想让它被斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不该被斩断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.豪火灭却
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火遁.爆风乱舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有鸣人的查克拉外衣保护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕会成烤全猪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的查克拉一直在保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么持续下去真的没关系吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了 逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才怪 赶紧找
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你想保护大家就只能防御了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直这样有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就操纵我输送给你的全部查克拉 太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会筋疲力尽的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且十尾好像在积蓄查克拉 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样只会越来越虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追求孤独的你大概不会明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的周围有一群同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我非常地高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭这点 力量就会源源不断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把同伴的死所带来的悲痛称作羁绊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没必要保护同伴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这只会诡辩的家伙瞎说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常讨厌你这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡扯了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想说的是 只要是为了同伴 无论多痛苦我都会忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会放弃这个信念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我真的很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是心中如果没了同伴 才是最令人痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带土 你想通过鸣人确认某些事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柱间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 要塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,压制不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然挣脱了利用鸣人的查克拉施展的山土之术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他的术能牵制它了 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾准备用天变地异了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天变…什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么悠闲了 会天崩地裂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为切断了我和十尾的唯一联系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我再也没法控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候变成人柱力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好戏现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要消灭十尾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎看准了这个时机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 这边就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了 天变地异
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下总该清扫了一些障碍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人又一次保护了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消退了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你没法继续逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也玩够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该退场了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 我们齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你恢复一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然内心迷茫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止 你如果想杀我早该得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然会在战场上对敌人心生怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为内疚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有保护好凛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有遵守答应我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以心怀内疚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我洗心革面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带土 这一切该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾经的梦想是当上火影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人现在也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的话和你之前说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宇智波带土 一定要成为火影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我的影岩一定要雕上护目镜和写轮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的梦想是当上火影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还要让村民们认同我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉间 你将过去的自己和鸣人重叠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鸣人现在的话当做自己曾经的话来听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望被曾经的自己否定 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该明白鸣人的想法才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回头还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新变回那时的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为我十分了解鸣人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才倾听他的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后全盘否定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带土…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我心存内疚根本就是愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你认为我发起战争是因为你和凛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛是自己冲向了你的雷切 自己选择了死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛被雾隐村掳走 成为了三尾人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你成功夺回了凛 并将她带了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可这原本就是雾隐的作战方案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你们逃回木叶 假装一路追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等增援部队到了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾隐抓走了凛 想让她成为某个实验体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被带入血雾之村 基本就没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通灵之术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得凛的味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增援部队到达后转告他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去追凛了 先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是木叶…木叶的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 就这样引开敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在这里待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被幻术夺去了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们撤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虏和他们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后牵制敌人的任务就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 情况不妙我们自然会撤的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西 我似乎…有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到身体里有些其他东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾隐的忍者好像对我施展了某种仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种特别的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我那时失去了意识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难缠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西 马上杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去…我可能会袭击木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我答应带土要保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能杀你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有什么其他方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先回村子再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来牵制他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾隐计划在凛回到村子后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便驱使她体内的三尾失控 从而袭击木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.05,0:18:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛明白他们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用你向敌人施展雷切的一瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…自我牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决心死在所爱之人的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言…没有保护好凛的你是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛在我心中是不该死去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 死去的凛也是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛只有活着才是凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致这种状况的是忍者的体系 村子以及忍者们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界的本身才让我感到绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个虚假的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中若无同伴才是最痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将你当时的话原封不动地转达给了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的你一定能和鸣人感同身受 并说出那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今 我依旧这么认为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的内心空无一物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连痛苦都感觉不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用内疚 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个空洞便是被这地狱般的世界打开的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的我 心中只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我才舍弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也一直被痛苦煎熬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在凛的墓前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的墓前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用再痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言 理想中的我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成为火影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渴望并喜欢的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个幻术世界中全都能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你心中的空洞立刻就会被填满
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能填补心中的空洞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要连凛生前的回忆都抹除掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是凛牺牲了自己去保护村子所留下的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己用再多的妄想也不可能填补心中的空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幻术世界中又有何不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实太过残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让心中的空洞不断扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事就是不遂人愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些人就是来不及伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我所经历的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同我没来得及救琳一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集的火影疾风传是 填平之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧 卡卡西
